HYPERION JUICER: Next-generation Juicer, faster burnout

A next-generation Juicer running enhanced combat stimulants for even
greater physical ability, at a steeper price in lifespan. Hyperion
Juicers are the pinnacle of chemical enhancement: faster, stronger,
and more deadly than standard models, but burning out even faster.

Hyperion Juicers gain superior combat bonuses, higher HP per level,
and a broader weapon proficiency selection. Acrobatics and gymnastics
training make them exceptional in close quarters. Skill picks come
from Physical, Espionage, Military, Pilot, and W.P. categories.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: PS 12, PE 12.
  Equipment: Hyperion Juicer harness (military grade, fitted), medium
    body armor, three weapons, and one year enhanced drug supply.

